Summary:	X11 composite manager
Name:		xcompmgr
Version:	1.1.8
Release:	1%{?dist}
License:	Copyright only
URL:		http://xapps.freedesktop.org
Source0:	https://www.x.org/archive/individual/app/%{name}-%{version}.tar.gz
